#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/best-practices-sampling-event-planned-additions.adoc:59
msgid "#TODO:# Provide a recommendation on how to publish data produced from large projects. The current recommendation is to publish a single dataset, because dividing it into multiple datasets results in more duplication of effort entering metadata. Publishers insisting on publishing multiple datasets should link them using Project.ID in EML."
msgstr "#TODO:# 提供建議如何發布由大型專案產生的資料。目前的建議是發布單一資料集，因為將其分為多個資料集會增加重複填寫詮釋資料的工作量。堅持發布多個資料集的發布者應使用 Project.ID 在 EML 中連結它們。"

